ng/></usg><quote>brigadtæ kærægemæ fæsseduncæ erisæj</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>бригады вызывают друг друга на соревнование</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>teams challenge each other to the competition</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_FS"/><biblScope>I 6</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>jarəš</w> <gloss><q>состязание</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w/> <gloss><q>соревнование</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Сюда же <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>(i)erisi</w> <gloss><q>сражение</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/> <gloss><q>атака</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/> <w>erəš</w> <gloss><q>упорный</q></gloss></mentioned>. Первоисточником является, вероятно, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>ερις</w> <gloss><q>спор</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w/> <gloss><q>состязание</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w>ερίζω</w> <gloss><q>спорю</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w/> <gloss><q>состязаюсь</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>jarəš</w> <gloss><q>contest</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w/> <gloss><q>competition</q></gloss></mentioned>, . <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>(i)erisi</w> <gloss><q>battle</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/> <gloss><q>attack</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/> <w>erəš</w> <gloss><q>pertinacious</q></gloss></mentioned> are related to it as well. The primary source is probably <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>ερις</w> <gloss><q>bet</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w/> <gloss><q>contest</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w>ερίζω</w> <gloss><q>I bet</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><w/> <gloss><q>I compete</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>